An investigation failed to reveal any invitation extended to Mr. Nixon during the period when Oswald's threat reportedly occurred.
he was not actually planning to shoot Mr. Nixon at that time in Dallas.
there is no question that in this incident it was a question of Mr. Nixon, end quote.
When asked later whether it might have been Mr. Johnson, she said, quote, Yes, no.
I am getting a little confused with so many questions.
